headline: 3 High-Yielding Dividend Stocks That Should Pay You Forever
summary: Holding shares of strong companies that pay consistent dividends can help you preserve and grow your savings.  Three Motley Fool contributors recently selected their favorite high-yield dividend stocks to buy now.  Here's why they think Target (NYSE: TGT), General Mills (NYSE: GIS), and British American Tobacco (NYSE: BTI) could pay you passive income forever.
